document.full_text: former world champion tyson gay said he was unlikely to run the 200 meters at this month's u.s. trials, effectively ending his chances of facing world record holder usain bolt over the distance at this year's world championships in south korea.
document.title: tyson gay unlikely to run 200m at u.s. trials
lines_and_colors: former world champion tyson gay said he was unlikely to run the 200 meters at this month's u.s. trials, effectively ending his chances of facing world record holder usain bolt over the distance at this year's world championships in south korea.
